        excerpt: 'From agentic AI to multimodal models, 2026 marks a step-change in what enterprise AI can accomplish.',
        body: `<p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">2026 is a landmark year for enterprise AI. Here are the five trends every business leader should understand and act on right now.</p>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-3 mt-7">1. Agentic AI Systems</h3>
<p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">AI agents that can autonomously plan multi-step tasks — browsing the web, writing code, calling APIs, and reporting results — are moving from labs into production. Early adopters report 5× productivity gains in knowledge work.</p>
